c: 42
v: 22
t: "(Ku lunaku olwo) oliraba abeeyisa obubi nga beraliikirira olwebyo bye bakola, era nga ddala ekyo kigenda kubatuukako ate abo abakkiriza ne bakola emirimu emirongoofu balibeera mu bifo byo mu jjana, balifuna ebyo bye baliyagala ewa Mukama omulabirizi waabwe, ekyo kyo, bwe bulungi obusuffu"